[Constants]
switchAttack = 220 ; ANIM: Switch attack. 
I highly recommend to clone your favorite animation in Fighter Factory and extend the frametime of the animelem that has the red box.
switchAirAttack = 611 ; ANIM: switch air attack.
snapBackAttack = 300 ; ANIM: snapback attack
snapBackHit = 228 ; this is the ANIMATION used when the char get hit by the snapback attack
StateTagAssistSuper = 567891 ; STATENO: normal assist attack
StateTagAssistHyper = 567891 ; STATENO: Super assist attack, cost 1500 of power.
tauntWhileWaitingForPartners = 195 ; ANIM: If mvc1switch is on, taunt after switch. Used on switch attack or triple menace.


[Quotes]
victory0 = "Work at it. All I can do is work hard! That's the story of my life!"
victory1 = "I can do it. I know I can do it. I'm the guy who gets it done, broken bones or not. No matter what, I can do it! I can fight!"
victory2 = "The strong should aid and protect the weak. Then, the weak will become strong and they, in turn, will aid and protect those weaker than them. That is the law of nature."
victory3 = "Not today or anytime in future! Even I'm broken, I will never give up no matter what!"
victory4 = "Thank you, Yoriichi, Father, and my family. Your technique has helped me prevail!"

